data.text:
“Long has mankind seen strange things and fantastical worlds in hallucinations and dreams. Those who have learned to transverse the ether may step between these worlds and see things few have. A tear in the fabric of time, a blue matter rift, or a conjured magic portal may be your gateway to worlds beyond your imagining.”

Steam Powered Giraffe is a musical pantomime troupe of malfunctioning singing robots originally built in 1896. This unofficial wiki is a compendium of the mythos, characters, and worlds found in the SPG universe through their songs and fiction, alongside information on the group and their discography.
